name: HiD(HolditDown)(Ucf)
0:
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
H.i.D. Hold it down provides a sort of life guide we wish we had throughout our college careers. 

We are a high end brand that specializes in environmentally friendly apparel. We chose the name H.i.D. because we stand for supporting those around you whether it be a partner, friend or a family member, and so we have created this flash briefing to help bring support to those that hold it down.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
